    </div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Every&nbsp;Other&nbsp;Day</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP-507&nbsp;Tale</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>This was made very quickly after a walk. It’s weird, but I haven’t deleted it yet, so, you know. It’s about the banality of anomalousness, and stuff. 507 goes through different worlds, some of which are just weird, but most of which are normal. When it says &quot;his&quot; in some places, that’s because in those universes, those belong to parallel hims, and aren’t just separate points in one universe. That’s what it’s about, you see, but it could maybe have also served as an allegory or something? I dunno. Check it out, if you haven’t, you tell me about it.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2525&nbsp;N&nbsp;Waterworks&nbsp;St</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Lambda-5&nbsp;Tale</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Remember what I said about the diligence and time put into 2446? Yeah, this was built out of the corpse of a half-finished tale in the space of a few hours. There seems to be a pattern with that an my tales. The original tale would have started the same way, then ended with a long conversation with the reality-bender which was scrapped, mainly because I didn’t have enough time to polish it. I think it turned out somewhat okay in the end, if pretty quick and unproductive.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">My&nbsp;Loever,&nbsp;the&nbsp;Dog:&nbsp;The&nbsp;Incredibly&nbsp;True&nbsp;Story&nbsp;of&nbsp;Kain&nbsp;Pathos&nbsp;Crow</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">April&nbsp;Fools&nbsp;2016&nbsp;Crackfic</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>A tale about bestiality has won a contest on this site. How about that? <a href="/an-incredibly-important-announcement">Yes, it won.</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">rabbit&nbsp;here,&nbsp;rabbit&nbsp;there</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
